{"thag2.12:0.1":"Theragatha 2.12 ","thag2.12:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.12:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","thag2.12:0.4":"Jotidasattheragatha ","thag2.12:1.1":"“Ye kho te vethamissena, ","thag2.12:1.2":"nanattena ca kammuna; ","thag2.12:1.3":"Manusse uparundhanti, ","thag2.12:1.4":"pharusupakkama jana; ","thag2.12:1.5":"Tepi tattheva kiranti, ","thag2.12:1.6":"na hi kammam panassati. ","thag2.12:2.1":"Yam karoti naro kammam, ","thag2.12:2.2":"Kalyanam yadi papakam; ","thag2.12:2.3":"Tassa tasseva dayado, ","thag2.12:2.4":"Yam yam kammam pakubbati”ti. ","thag2.12:2.5":"… Jotidaso thero …. "}